Usage: ecoDeleteRepeater [-help] [-logicalChangeOnly] { -inst {list of instances} | -invPair {pairs of inverters} }

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
-inst {list of instances}               # Specifies names of instances to be
                                        # deleted/evaluated for deletion
                                        # (string, optional)
-invPair {pairs of inverters}           # Specifies pairs of inverters to be
                                        # deleted/evaluated for deletion
                                        # (string, optional)
-logicalChangeOnly                      # Specifies that buffer/inverter
                                        # deletion should be done in
                                        # logical-only mode (bool, optional)